description: Under normal circumstances, at least 80% of the fund's net assets, plus borrowings for investment purposes, will be invested in the component securities of the index. The index generally contains approximately 25 TopGun companies. To the extent the index concentrates (i.e., holds more than 25% of its total assets) in the securities of a particular industry, the fund will concentrate its investments to approximately the same extent as the index. It is non-diversified.
name: AXS Brendan Wood TopGun Index ETF
